{
  "stem": "7069.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And it certainly-- and the order was given that they are looking for 1,000 men that would be able to be mustered out for a work commando, to be taken out of the camp, not too far away, where they intend to build an airstrip.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "You see, the Nazis had been driven in from all sides.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "In the meantime, lost airfields, and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And of course we're still fighting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And they needed more airfields.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And so they started to muster out a thousand men.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And my brother said to me, look, you've got to try to hide this thing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Because you've got to come with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Because if we are separated, you know very well your situation is very, very hopeless this way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Which-- which was very cool.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And I knew it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I was fully aware of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I had no chance to survive for any length of time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "But anyways, so we went by the doctors, I tried to hide this thing, but the doctors noticed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And they didn't-- they sent my brother this way and kept me on the side of being kept in the camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Which turned out to be the most disastrous happening for us all the time when we were in the camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Yet, as you will see, that was, for us, the only way to survive, as it turns out to be.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Anyways, well, I can come to the reason right away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "It turns out to be that my brother is the only survivor of this 1,000-man commando.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "This 1,000-men commando was down to a size-- to a size, after four weeks, of 52 people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And my brother was able to escape the last moment, during one night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And he was taken in by a German farmer, who was obviously no Nazi.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
